archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: List of free graph visualization libraries
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation: From "The list of graph visualization libraries" by Elise Devaux, May 2019 at https://medium.com/@Elise_Deux/the-list-of-graph-visualization-libraries-7a7b89aab6a6 This list presents various graph (aka network) visualization libraries. Most of these libraries are free or open-source. A few are commercial products. There are mainly JavaScript libraries but you’ll also find other languages. The post lists libraries of various ‘depth’, some offering basic layouts and interaction, other more advanced customization and integration options.
